sdapy.read_default.get_keypairs¶

sdapy.read_default.get_keypairs(filename='auth.txt', wdir=None, verbose=False, return_comments=False, return_type=False)¶

get keypairs that would be used by online services, e.g. forced photometry

Parameters
filenamestr

file name

wdirstr

data directory, if None, will be set as HAFFET default data directory, i.e. $ZTFDATA

verbosebool

show report

return_commentsbool

if True, return comments of each parameters

return_typebool

if True, return types of each parameters

Returns
default_infosdict

HAFFET
